name: PORTALS 001
description:
Click for new portals. 
Skys are relative to your timezone and will gradually change during a 24-hour cycle. 
Skip through time zones with LEFT and RIGHT keyboard arrows. 
Reset back to your time zone with the UP keyboard arrow.

Animation, variable dimensions, generative, interactive - p5.js, HTML, CSS
Artist: Aleksandra Jovanic / @aleksandrajovanic  — October 2021
